{"tid":2277422,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民眾持械聚票站 恐成新常態","createTime":"2020-11-08T12:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T12:56:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d5271ef1b3925257d8ec67a715732361708e54cb","tid":2277422,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:39:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/FSSVT3NS4VDXDCYNJ6DQBEZEUA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2FFSSVT3NS4VDXDCYNJ6DQBEZEUA%2F&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq76zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=a73a8f39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2FFSSVT3NS4VDXDCYNJ6DQBEZEUA%2F&h=6291389b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/FSSVT3NS4VDXDCYNJ6DQBEZEUA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n民眾持械聚票站 恐成新常態<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5kQRktfONuCn0uoFV5alc_wK5vU=/720x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4ONKF6DIQFC4XPPEP23XMAQ32Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5kQRktfONuCn0uoFV5alc_wK5vU%3D%2F720x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4ONKF6DIQFC4XPPEP23XMAQ32Q.jpg&h=d1790fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■在底特律，有腰間亮出槍枝的民眾在點票中心外等候。路透社<br />\n<br />\n今屆美國大選出現一個過往鮮有的現象，就是多個城市都有民眾持槍在點票中心外聚集。專家憂慮票站「晒馬」已成新常態，終有一日會擦槍走火。<br />\n<br />\n這些持械示威者大多是特朗普的支持者，目前只佔少數，他們的武器有手槍、霰彈槍、甚至軍用的半自動步槍，部份人聲稱自己要「保護和平示威」和「確保所有合法選票獲點算」，。。。。。。。。。。，擔心這種以展示武力表態的現象會成為常態。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n極右組織QAnon涉運假票<br />\n<br />\n大選點票已經過逾四日，各搖擺州繼續有人示威，幸未釀成暴力衝突。在拜登已勝出的密歇根州，最大城市底特律有數百特朗普支持者持槍在點票中心外高叫「我們贏了」，迫。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n近日示威較值得關注的，是兩名來自維珍尼亞州、持AR步槍的男子上周四在費城一個票站外被捕，。。。。。。。。。。。，被指與一間特朗普團隊數碼總監科比（Gary Coby）營運的公司Opn Sesame有關。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡/美聯社"},{"pid":"a03157401c5b4aefd9a997bf080fdc066ec00221","tid":2277422,"uid":68598,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:40:11.000Z","msg":"然後最先開鎗既係blm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63625328adce3b95ea481cf86a81b230106a64d6","tid":2277422,"uid":58841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"但係最先開槍射侵粉係左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250e2733b0568b56abc137b9257a7138eb1f34a9","tid":2277422,"uid":264245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"63625328adce3b95ea481cf86a81b230106a64d6","tid":2277422,"uid":58841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"但係最先開槍射侵粉係左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:41:35.000Z","msg":"呢單周圍都比人censored<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a7b44cff3424dbebac93effb08b7e1c780f147","tid":2277422,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"250e2733b0568b56abc137b9257a7138eb1f34a9","tid":2277422,"uid":264245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"63625328adce3b95ea481cf86a81b230106a64d6","tid":2277422,"uid":58841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"但係最先開槍射侵粉係左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:41:35.000Z","msg":"呢單周圍都比人censored<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:42:14.000Z","msg":"蘋果其實係咪左到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e484de5150213590629a9315e398519e2a5448","tid":2277422,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:43:09.000Z","msg":"又係蘋果日報呢份死垃圾<br />\n忍撚左佢好耐"},{"pid":"342f49e21be4b957863080cfc38f79fa2d51d87d","tid":2277422,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63625328adc